    {
      "role": "user",
      "content": "it's just not about \"healing\" or \"time\" anymore. when you're at the top, you're a person. now, when I walk into a room, people just see the scandal. they see the failure. i look in the mirror and i don't even see a human being, just a walking cautionary tale. it feels like the version of me that actually mattered is dead, and this thing left behind is just waiting for the clock to run out.",
      "source": "evaluator"
    },
